{"id": "1424843520312737863", "channel_id": "1424843520312737863", "type": 0, "author_id": "640213495815733298", "author_name": "dusha_69", "author_bot": false, "content": "I wanted to ask about my nickname. The thing is, I recently had a nickname in Russian, then I changed it, and now I noticed that I can’t change it back because Russian characters are not allowed. Will this remain the case, or will the ability to create nicknames in Russian be restored?", "timestamp": "2025-10-06T19:39:27.555000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1424843520312737863", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Name change", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1424653673363013694", "channel_id": "1424653673363013694", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi! I'm a localization volunteer. I'm working on all of the EN Resonance effects, but I'm stuck at Chapter 3 because I don't know what to do about this contradictory information. The only data point I have right now is the current effect of the fully upgraded \"Mutated Heart\" so I need help confirming what the Primary version of it does.\n\n## What are the actual gameplay effects of these Resonances?\nMy theory is that when \"Defiant Will\" is at Lv.0 (unactivated), \"Mutated Heart\" would discard your hand (`X` cards), then draw that many cards (`X+0`), meaning the description of \"Strange Pustule\" is incorrect, but there's no way for me to prove this at all as I don't have access to the basic version of \"Mutated Heart\" anymore.\n\nAny number of things could potentially be incorrect, so I need evidence of what's wrong here. **Exactly what part of all of this is a bug?**", "timestamp": "2025-10-06T07:05:04.515000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-28T17:07:54.711000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1424653673748758602", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1858422, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1424653673363013694/1424653673748758602/image.png?ex=69cc1ae0&is=69cac960&hm=4d4ab11653e02a50003030e0b5d76a1aa51d88a31c24d254d7e7610a6521cd29&"}, {"id": "1424653674382360627", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1845941, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1424653673363013694/1424653674382360627/image.png?ex=69cc1ae0&is=69cac960&hm=6cecacd0b5dffa7b852c5b49a015185f46506669896dc5ce4aee3db9e2465195&"}, {"id": "1424653674734551122", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 176170, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1424653673363013694/1424653674734551122/image.png?ex=69cc1ae0&is=69cac960&hm=26108a6cbcd3cc8f07a59bf2e8793796c01caca66ed8a723fc60c5039e6ba1e8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1424653673363013694", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」How many cards does \"Mutated Heart\" draw without Resonances?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785", "1361168893200044183"]}
