{"id": "1424645808812195870", "channel_id": "1424375134168285215", "type": 19, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi! This isn't a bug~\nThis is because \"Steal\" is actually 2 effects in a trenchcoat:\n- Inflict 11 <:strdown:1408311306058203236>STR▼ on each enemy; and\n- Gain 11 <:str:1408311379932221450>STR for each enemy.\n\nEffects that increase one effect's value wouldn't increase the other, and it's important that the in-battle card descriptions properly communicate what the cards will do when played, so to be able to display the two values correctly, it was split into two effect descriptions. You'll notice if you look that there are A LOT of cards that are worded differently in the menu and in battle because of this.\n\nThis has, unfortunately, made the text of these cards so long as to completely obscure poor Tinct's face. Fixing this is high on my to-do list when I can get to it, but I'm only one volunteer, and it's a big project 😅", "timestamp": "2025-10-06T06:33:49.460000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-06T15:51:27.337000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["251265827267936257"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1424375134168285215", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1424375134168285215", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "The \"Steal\" keyword isn't used during gameplay", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169144216686744"]}
{"id": "1424653928431358053", "channel_id": "1424375134168285215", "type": 19, "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "author_bot": false, "content": "what is you assigned work? maybe we can assist", "timestamp": "2025-10-06T07:06:05.328000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["183782216353054720"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1424645808812195870", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1424375134168285215", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "The \"Steal\" keyword isn't used during gameplay", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169144216686744"]}
{"id": "1424655245140557929", "channel_id": "1424375134168285215", "type": 19, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "Thanks for the offer, but I can't share any work with anyone that hasn't been confirmed for the volunteer project. <:shrug:1003188954218123314> Try reaching out to <@1376763322568937562> to see if you can apply and join if you want to help out!", "timestamp": "2025-10-06T07:11:19.256000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-06T07:11:53.750000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["244028747999608832", "1376763322568937562"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1424653928431358053", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1424375134168285215", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "The \"Steal\" keyword isn't used during gameplay", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169144216686744"]}
